; Coverage test for xact.cc
; Tests the error when an automated transaction's posting has no amount
; and no amount expression.

= /Expenses:Food/
    Expenses:Tax

2024/01/01 Groceries
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 10:
While applying automated transaction from "$FILE", lines 5-6:
> = /Expenses:Food/
>     Expenses:Tax
While extending transaction from "$FILE", lines 8-10:
> 2024/01/01 Groceries
>     Expenses:Food    $10.00
>     Assets:Cash
Error: Automated transaction's posting has no amount
end test
